snippet.title: Shadow Warrior 3 | March 1 | PS4 XB1 & PC
snippet.description:
Preorder now to get the tentacled Koromodako Katana skin plus preorders on PS and Xbox instantly unlock Shadow Warrior 1 and 2 for free: http://shadowwarrior.com

Shadow Warrior 3, a stunning new entry in the global best-selling franchise, will launch its barrage of over-the-top weapons and offbeat humor on March 1.

Visit shadowwarrior.com and follow @ShadowWarrior on Twitter for more on Lo Wang's next great adventure!
